==English==

===Etymology===
Related to {{G.}} ''[[Lenz]]'' "springtime", which is derived from a word related to [[long]], because of the longer days.

===Proper noun===
'''Lent''' <!-- capitalized, but is it a proper noun? Yes, like Christmas -->
# Period of [[penitence]] for Christians before [[Easter]].

